DM3AUD.original: ~z~Derrick fucking set me up in the first place.
~z~But you came. I do have friends. I do.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~But you came. I do have friends. I do.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright man, get these guys, will ya?
~z~It's about bloody time. I been in there doing a stretch I didn't deserve for too long.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~It's about bloody time. I been in there doing a stretch I didn't deserve for too long.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Hey Buddy, get this thing outta the road, will you?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，伙计，麻烦你把车开走，好吗？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~People remember you alright. You're at the front of certain people's minds.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~是有人记着你。那人很惦记你的。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I do not like to kill unarmed men.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I do not like to kill unarmed men.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I got a bad feeling about this.
~z~He's a rat, Derrick McReary. Always has been always will be.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~他才是叛徒，Derrick McReary。过去是，以后也是。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You boys, you boys... who sent you?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~You boys, you boys... who sent you?

DM3AUD.original: ~z~But it ain't like I'm going to put a weapon in his hand just so I can pop him, is it? You do what you got to do.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~But it ain't like I'm going to put a weapon in his hand just so I can pop him, is it? You do what you got to do.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Release the handbrake, Packie. We need to get rid of the van as well.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Release the handbrake, Packie. We need to get rid of the van as well.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Who is it then, who do I got to thank?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Who is it then, who do I got to thank?

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Niko, I hear my brother Derrick is asking you to ice his old drinking buddy, Aiden O'Malley?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，听说我哥哥Derrick让你去做掉他的老酒友Aiden O'Malley？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~It's a surprise. Wait until we get to the cliffs. You'll find out then.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~It's a surprise. Wait until we get to the cliffs. You'll find out then.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You boys have got to know about giving it back to someone as good as they gave it to you.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~You boys have got to know about giving it back to someone as good as they gave it to you.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Thank Christ, the Virgin and every damn saint who ever walked on God's green Earth for you guys.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Thank Christ, the Virgin and every damn saint who ever walked on God's green Earth for you guys.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Hey buddy, we're gonna need you to move this thing.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，伙计，我们需要你把车挪开。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Don't think about it, man, he was a rat. I don't believe a word he said about Derrick. He's fish food.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Don't think about it, man, he was a rat. I don't believe a word he said about Derrick. He's fish food.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~She stopped writing and coming on visiting days but I could tell she was still thinking of me. I knew it.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~她确实不给我写信也不来探监了，不过她一定还想着我。我就知道。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I went into a situation full of optimism, full of naiveté...
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我曾经就有过盲目乐观的单纯岁月...

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Niko, get rid of dear old Aiden...
~z~Drive the van, Niko. I'll handle the prisoner.
~z~I'd been praying to be rescued since the first day they incarcerated me in that God forsaken place.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I'd been praying to be rescued since the first day they incarcerated me in that God forsaken place.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Well, hurry up and do it already.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Well, hurry up and do it already.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Or doing a kind turn for someone who's helped you out in the past. That's what this is about, isn't it?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Or doing a kind turn for someone who's helped you out in the past. That's what this is about, isn't it?

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Okay, it looks like we've lost them. Take us over to the cliffs in Leftwood.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，应该甩掉他们了。带我们去Leftwood的悬崖。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We better split up so the cops don't make us for what went down in the tunnel.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~We better split up so the cops don't make us for what went down in the tunnel.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I ain't gonna be around much longer at this rate. Fucking help me!
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~再这样下去我可撑不住。快他妈支援我。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I thank ya, boys. I thank ya with all me heart.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I thank ya, boys. I thank ya with all me heart.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Christ, someone knows. Someone cares about old Aiden O'Malley. I knew someone had to care.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Christ, someone knows. Someone cares about old Aiden O'Malley. I knew someone had to care.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You've made me a happy man, boys. Now it's time to tell me who asked you to do this.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~你们让我的日子又快活了，孩子们。现在该告诉我是谁让你们这么做了吧。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We need to lose this van, Packie. The cops'll be looking for it.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们得把这辆车处理掉，Packie。条子会一直找它的。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me. Aiden O'Malley sprung from the joint. Wait until this gets around the yard.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Fuck me. Aiden O'Malley sprung from the joint. Wait until this gets around the yard.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~So you thought you'd talk about him? He's my brother, and guys like you are killin' him!
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~就你还能对他说三道四？他是我哥哥，你这样的人都要害死他了。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You're not free yet, asshole. Get in that car!
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~你还没自由呢，混蛋。给我上车！

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Let alone eaten another prison meal or taken another fucking shower.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Let alone eaten another prison meal or taken another fucking shower.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~They ain't gonna break this perp out on our watch.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~有我们在，他们别想救走这个囚犯。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Just to be outta these clothes, to be able to get up when I want to get up and walk where I want to walk.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Just to be outta these clothes, to be able to get up when I want to get up and walk where I want to walk.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~When we have them blocked in, we take down the escort and make off with the prisoner.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~堵住他们以后，我们就干掉护卫，带着囚犯逃跑。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I hope you can deal with Aiden still being out there.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I hope you can deal with Aiden still being out there.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Look at me... like smack on a fucking spoon.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~看看我...就他妈像勺子上的可卡因。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Name Derrick McReary ring any bells? He's my brother.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Derrick McReary这名儿有印象吗？他是我哥哥。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Is that why you were in the cop shop? Trying to find another way out of the penal system?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Is that why you were in the cop shop? Trying to find another way out of the penal system?

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Okay, man. First thing we gotta do is dump this prison van. Cops'll be looking.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，兄弟。我们要做的第一件事就是扔了这辆囚车。条子会来找的。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Don't let them get this perp outta here.
~z~Good, because I couldn't catch the prison van.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Good, because I couldn't catch the prison van.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, Niko. Now that we lost 'em we gotta go out to the cliffs in Leftwood.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，Niko。既然已经甩掉了他们，我们就该去Leftwood的悬崖了。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I thought I was out. I thought I was liberated.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~靠，我还以为我出来了。我还以为我自由了。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Who knows? Anyway, the convoy with O'Malley in it has to go through the Booth Tunnel.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~谁知道呢？反正押送O'Malley的车队必定会经过Booth隧道。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~where he's been talking shit about me,
~z~Someone who feels you should get what you deserve.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Someone who feels you should get what you deserve.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We've got rid of the unwanted attention. Now it's time for business. Get us to the cliffs in Leftwood.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~甩掉这帮多余的人了。现在该做正事了，带我们去Leftwood的悬崖。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Okay, Derrick. I'll call you again when it's done.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Okay, Derrick. I'll call you again when it's done.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You're gonna get there first and block the road with your truck.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~你要抢先到达那里，然后用卡车封路。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~That's probably what Derrick would have told you to do in his smacked out state.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~也就吸毒吸昏头的Derrick会让你这么做。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, alright. I'll try to lose these fucking cops.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，好了，我会尽量甩掉这些傻逼条子的。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I don't want to die, I've been rotting in prison for years. I don't want to die.Please, I just want to be free.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我不想死，我都在监狱里烂了这么多年了。我不想死。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I left a truck with a rocket launcher in it for ya in an alley, off of Applewhite in Alderney City.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我在一条巷子里给你留了辆装有火箭发射器的卡车，~n~在Alderney市的Applewhite街上。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Shake these cops, Niko. We need them to think Aiden is free as a fucking bird.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~甩掉这些条子，Niko。我们要让他们认为Aiden现在跟小鸟一样自在。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Please, Niko, boy... just this last one... please?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~拜托了，Niko，孩子...就这最后一次...拜托了？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Aiden's being moved by van from the bacon factory,
~z~Yeah, he has, what's the big deal?
~z~Problem is, he's the first one they'd talk to if that happened. We got to make this look like a prison break.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~问题在于，真那样的话，警察第一个就会找他问话。我们得把它演成劫囚。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~He's the reason I ended up in that place to start with, the spineless...
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~一开始我会进去就是因为他，这没骨气的...

DM3AUD.original: ~z~The way I got treated in there by the warden, by the screws, by every fucking inmate in the joint.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~The way I got treated in there by the warden, by the screws, by every fucking inmate in the joint.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Christ, we can't make him disappear now.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~上帝啊，现在我们没法让他消失了。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~The whiskey, the women, every fucking thing a free man takes for granted.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~The whiskey, the women, every fucking thing a free man takes for granted.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Come on, buddy you're going to have to move this thing.
~z~They're making a play for the prisoner. Defend the stockade.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~他们是冲着犯人来的。保护囚车。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Damn right, somewhere the cops'll never find me.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~太他妈对了，去个条子永远找不到我的地方。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~back to the Alderney State Correctional Facility.
~z~O'Malley is in government custody. He's got more police protection than the mayor.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~O'Malley现在受政府羁押，保护他的警察比保护市长的还多。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Get rid of this attention, Niko. We don't want anyone after us while we're doing what we gotta do.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~摆脱通缉，Niko。我们可不想在做正事的时候被人追着。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~A truck with a rocket launcher in it? What am I meant to do with them?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~装着火箭发射器的卡车？我要这些有什么用？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Lose the cops. I'll try to lose the fucking cops.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Lose the cops. I'll try to lose the fucking cops.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Derrick, Packie is going to help me on this job. He's going to help me get Aiden O'Malley.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Derrick, Packie is going to help me on this job. He's going to help me get Aiden O'Malley.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~The cliffs of Leftwood then. Is there a boat coming or something? Where am I going?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Leftwood的悬崖是吧。那边有船来接吗？我会去哪儿？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Hold tight, back up is on it's way.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Hold tight, back up is on it's way.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~So you thought you'd rat him out? This is the last sunset you're ever going to see. Enjoy it...
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~所以你就觉得你也能卖了他？这是你能看见的最后一次日落了。好好享受吧...

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Great. They're leaving the old cop shop now, should be at the Booth Tunnel soon.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~好了。他们从老警局出发了，很快就会到Booth隧道。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Nobody's going to find you where you're going, friend.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~你要去的地方没人能找到你，朋友。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We got to lose this heat before we can send this fucker where he's going.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们得先把条子甩了，才能把这逼送到该去的地方。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You're going to a faraway place, my friend.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~你要去一个遥远的地方，我的朋友。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Disappear, prisoner. Your old life is over. It's time to start a new one.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Disappear, prisoner. Your old life is over. It's time to start a new one.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We will not lose a prisoner on my watch.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~We will not lose a prisoner on my watch.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~That wasn't about getting out, that was pay back.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~That wasn't about getting out, that was pay back.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, they're sending fucking choppers after us.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Shit, they're sending fucking choppers after us.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You and me, we're the same. The same.
~z~I woulda done anything to get out.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I woulda done anything to get out.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Why don't we just kill the fucker there and then?
~z~The cliffs... the sea air... I really am free. I could cry.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~悬崖...海风...我真的自由了。我都要哭了。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Get rid of the escort, Niko. Come on.
~z~This is a fucking miracle. Shit, I'm free. I've imagined this day for years.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~This is a fucking miracle. Shit, I'm free. I've imagined this day for years.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~not that stale shit they pump though the correctional facility air conditioning units.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~not that stale shit they pump though the correctional facility air conditioning units.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Fuck, boys. I ain't doing too good over here.
~z~Good, good. Make him pay, Niko. Make him pay for the shit he's been talking.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Good, good. Make him pay, Niko. Make him pay for the shit he's been talking.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Lose 'em before I lose my fucking mind, okay?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Lose 'em before I lose my fucking mind, okay?

DM3AUD.original: ~z~How does a decent criminal stand a chance of losing the cops when they send choppers after him?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~How does a decent criminal stand a chance of losing the cops when they send choppers after him?

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Thanks. Maybe a clean break is in order. A fresh beginning.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~谢了，也许就此一刀两断比较合适。全新的开始。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We ain't letting this one get away.
~z~Who knows where I'm heading but it ain't Alderney. Maybe I'll go west. Follow the setting sun.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Who knows where I'm heading but it ain't Alderney. Maybe I'll go west. Follow the setting sun.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna come in from the rear and block 'em that way. Pick up the truck and gimme a call.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我就从后面跟进来，断了他们的后路。拿到卡车后给我打个电话。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~He's the reason I ended up in that place to start with, the spineless...
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~一开始我会进去就是因为他，这没骨气的...

DM3AUD.original: ~z~That's what I want, sea air. Thank you, boys. Thank you.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~That's what I want, sea air. Thank you, boys. Thank you.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~This ain't my idea of fun, boys. Would ya give me a hand?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~这跟我那种乐子不太一样，小子。麻烦您老帮个忙好吗？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, the cops have got choppers in the sky. That's fucking cheating.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Shit, the cops have got choppers in the sky. That's fucking cheating.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~The cliffs... the sea air... I really am free. I could cry.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~悬崖...海风...我真的自由了。我都要哭了。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~That's the end of a chapter. I can close the book on a whole lot of my past now Niko.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~这章终于完结了。~n~现在我可以合上这本写满我过去的书了，Niko。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~The cops is gonna know it wasn't a prison break when they find Aiden. Shit. I'll call Derrick.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~条子找到Aiden就会发现这不是一次劫狱了。操。我给Derrick打个电话。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I think we might have a problem here.
~z~I knew that no matter how long I rotted in there, people on the outside world still remember me.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我就知道不论要在里面烂上多久，外面总有人记着我的。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Who fucking knows? Today is the first day of the rest of my life.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Who fucking knows? Today is the first day of the rest of my life.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I need you to clear the area for us, Niko.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我需要你替我们杀出一条路来，Niko。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I tell you, you go into them showers clean and you come out dirty. You catch my drift, son?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I tell you, you go into them showers clean and you come out dirty. You catch my drift, son?

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Fuck, the sea air. To inhale the sea air,
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Fuck, the sea air. To inhale the sea air,

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Why? Why? Why, in God's name, why?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~为什么？为什么？为什么，上帝啊，为什么？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I don't think I coulda spent another night in the joint.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I don't think I coulda spent another night in the joint.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I don't know that I got off so lightly.
~z~You drive while I watch our cargo, Niko.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~你开车，我去看着我们的货物，Niko。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Niko. Will you handle these boys?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我操，Niko。你能不能解决这些人啊？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Hey Mitch, can you find out what this guy's up to?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，Mitch，你能去看看这人想干嘛吗？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I don't even know who sent you guys. Who do I got to thank for springing me from the joint?
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~靠，都不知道你们是谁派的。我要感谢哪位大哥出手相助？

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Now this is a piece of luck. Things are looking up. Looking up alright.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Now this is a piece of luck. Things are looking up. Looking up alright.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~A lot of people need a fresh start, I hope you make the most of yours.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~A lot of people need a fresh start, I hope you make the most of yours.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, man. We're coming to ya. Take out the escort but keep Derrick's pal alive.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~好的，兄弟。我这边快到了。干掉护卫，但别伤着Derrick的旧友。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We're doing this on behalf of an old acquaintance of yours.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们是替你的一个故交做这事的。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~We got to ditch this truck. It don't exactly blend in.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~我们得把囚车处理了。这样太显眼了。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Shit. The Aryan Brotherhood are going to be pissed, that's for damn sure. Sprung.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Shit. The Aryan Brotherhood are going to be pissed, that's for damn sure. Sprung.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Fucking get rid of these guys, Niko.
~z~They're making a play for the prisoner.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~They're making a play for the prisoner.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You've made me a happy man, boys. Now it's time to tell me who asked you to do this.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~你们让我的日子又快活了，孩子们。现在该告诉我是谁让你们这么做了吧。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~This is our prisoner, you will not take him.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~This is our prisoner, you will not take him.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Thanks. Maybe a clean break is in order. A fresh beginning.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~谢了，也许就此一刀两断比较合适。全新的开始。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~A damn fucking road block. This is gonna hurt.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~A damn fucking road block. This is gonna hurt.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~I nearly gave up hoping. I nearly lost faith.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~I nearly gave up hoping. I nearly lost faith.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Please, I just want to be free.
~z~Well, Derrick's going to be relieved. Thanks for doing that, Niko.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Well, Derrick's going to be relieved. Thanks for doing that, Niko.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~For the grace of God, all but for the grace of God I coulda died in there.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~For the grace of God, all but for the grace of God I coulda died in there.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~That's the end of a chapter. I can close the book on a whole lot of my past now Niko.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~这章终于完结了。~n~现在我可以合上这本写满我过去的书了，Niko。

DM3AUD.original: ~z~Trust the LCP-fucking-D to block the damn road.
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~Trust the LCP-fucking-D to block the damn road.

DM3AUD.original: ~z~You'll find out who it was when we get there. In the mean time, shut the hell up buddy!
DM3AUD.translated: ~z~到地方以后你就知道是谁了。至于现在，麻烦您老先闭上嘴！
